{"tid":2155830,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有個朋友做層壓式推銷做到好似吸毒咁","createTime":"2020-08-14T05:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T02:24:38.000Z","uid":317995,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2e9a79bc2ebfb7ff1824dd7bbdd26a034282b254","tid":2155830,"uid":317995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:03:20.000Z","msg":"近排開fb見到有個朋友日日post自己個網店有幾成功<br />\n再睇一睇原來係層推式推銷<br />\n每日叫人係佢網店買野(水解膠原蛋白)<br />\n又話可以草分,又話D 營養產品有幾有用<br />\n每個星期又話咩紅色主題,又黃色主題,又綠色主題<br />\n自己化個紅色妝,黃色妝,綠色妝,再加上一樣顏色既產品<br />\n佢已經比人洗左腦咁日日post相影自己D&quot;產品&quot;<br />\n最恐怖係佢老公都可以唔反對地自己都飲埋一份<br />\n日日飲D不明來歷既貴價謍養液<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7AmdDBC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7AmdDBC.jpg&h=6d69d38b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>我個朋友係咪已經無得救</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d748dc8b9c6482f7239afca9994bc3443619fd0a","tid":2155830,"uid":56550,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:06:15.000Z","msg":"冇得救 最後一定失去所有"},{"pid":"11c7056240cf7d669bd064073d437076d0a18d23","tid":2155830,"uid":317995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d748dc8b9c6482f7239afca9994bc3443619fd0a","tid":2155830,"uid":56550,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:06:15.000Z","msg":"冇得救 最後一定失去所有"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:15:40.000Z","msg":"佢依家每個月又話自己開始咩減肥方程式<br />\n唔洗做運動,唔洗食減肥餐單<br />\n只要飲佢既營養液就會減到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但個個月身形依然一樣<br />\n真係好想幫佢拉返出黎,見到佢咁樣真係好擔心"},{"pid":"bbefbbae2e119c1429181b5f1cad1ce651578b59","tid":2155830,"uid":38646,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:47:27.000Z","msg":"Natural selection <br />\n唔仆一次街佢唔會醒"},{"pid":"996b77ecc6111f25f4746786b5db4